disable

allow

prefer

require

 - Chose this mode to always require encryption. If the source database server does not support encryption, connection will fail


verify-ca

 - Chose this mode to always require encryption and to verify that the source database server has a valid SSL certificate


verify-full

 - This is the most secure mode. Chose this mode to always require encryption and to verify the identity of the source database server
